<author>ʿzmy ywsf, wjyh whbẗ</author>
<title>lys sẖyʾ yfṣlny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- lys sẖyʾuⁿ yfṣlny .. ʿn mḥbẗ ạlmsyḥ
 fḥyạty bʿd jhdiⁿ .. fy ḥmạh tstryḥ
 1- ạ̉ḥbny ạ̉ḥbh .. ysr by ạ̉sẖdw lh
 lạ hdẖạ ly wdẖạ lh .. fkl sẖyʾiⁿ mlkh
 rwḥy wnfsy wḥyạty .. tsẖhd ʿn ḥbh
 2- wlạ rjwʿ llwrạʾ .. fạlwrạʾ kạlʿdm
 wlạ ḥnyn llẓlạm .. qd mḍy̱ ʿhd ạlẓlm
 wkl sẖyʾiⁿ fy wjwdy .. ytgẖny̱ mn qdm</lyrics>
</song>